data.description: SELLER VERY MOTIVATED AND IT HAS TO GO-BRING US OFFERS! Will consider seller paid closing costs for loan costs or buy down rate- Just bring your ideas and let’s talk! READY FOR QUICK CLOSE! Location is fantastic for investment or rental. Blocks from CMU and OAE grade school, 10 minutes to airport and about 5 minutes to St Mary's Or VA Hospitals and downtown Grand Junction! At less than $300k this clean, move in ready home with newer laminate and carpet flooring makes a great investment or affordable option for those wanting a smaller home! Fenced front and back yard, attached garage, all appliances stay including washer and dryer and the extra working fridge in garage. 2 bedrooms, master with attached 3/4 bath. The full bath also attached to second bedroom and accessed by hall so makes for rental/ roommate accommodations!
